1.  1,000 needles procured and purchased; 
2.  500 rolls of sewing threads procured and purchased; 
3.  250 thatched mats (Kirintim) procured and purchased; 
4.  10,000 jute bags procured and purchased;
5.  500 water buckets procured and purchased;
6.  500 knives procured and purchased;
7.  125 heavy duty tarpaulins sheets (Lonas) procured and purchased;
8. 923 bars of soap procured and purchased;
9. 422 containers (5L) of bleach procured and purchased;
10. 250 sanitary kits procured and purchased;
11. 250 bags of rice (50kg) procured and purchased;
12. 87.5 bags of sugar (50kg) procured and purchased;
13. 250 containers (5L) of cooking oil procured and purchased;
14. 12,000 masks procured and purchased.

